latestPosts.caption:
8-Year Journey of Growth

🙏 Thank You, Mahadev: I’m truly grateful for your blessings and support along the way. You’ve been my strength.

💪 Hard Work: My brother @aman_gaurr (Nothing without him) and I have worked really hard. Every late night and early morning has paid off.

🎤 TEDx Opportunity: Speaking at TEDx as an entrepreneur is a huge moment for me. It’s amazing to share our story.

🌟 Lessons Learned: This journey has changed me in so many ways. Each challenge and success has helped me grow, and I’m so thankful for that.

I hustle every day for something bigger than this. I’m excited and hopeful as I look for new opportunities, working hard for my dreams. This journey means so much to me, and I can’t wait to see what’s next.🙏

latestPosts.caption: Every time you need me i am here 🙋❤️

Finally, my brother got ROKAFIED😭❤️ — and I got a best friend for life @bakshi_rijul .
My eyes were full of tears watching my two cuties walk in hand in hand. It’s a night I’ll never forget… and I know many more sleepless, joy filled nights are waiting for us.
None of this would’ve been possible without my people — my friends, or better yet my chosen family🥺😘
Also… we barely took any pictures, so please, treasure the few we have ( sabne zada peeli thi😒😂)
